<p>Hello <%= @resource.handle %>!</p>

<p>Someone--hopefully you--asked for a link to change your password on RecipePower. In the spirit of tireless dedication you expect from us, here it is:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @token, mode: :modal) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
